[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "The human mind has an adequate knowledge of the eternal and infinite essence of God.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Many errors, in truth, can be traced to this head, namely, that we do not apply names to things rightly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "So again, when men make mistakes in calculation, they have one set of figures in their mind, and another on the paper.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "If we could see into their minds, they do not make a mistake; they seem to do so, because we think, that they have the same numbers in their mind as they have on the paper.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "For by ideas I do not mean images such as are formed at the back of the eye, or in the midst of the brain, but the conceptions of thought.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "There is in the mind no volition or affirmation and negation, save that which an idea, inasmuch as it is an idea, involves.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000009_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Again, this idea of a triangle must involve this same affirmation, namely, that its three interior angles are equal to two right angles.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Wherefore, a false idea, inasmuch as it is false, does not involve certainty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "note).",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Thus, although the man be assumed to acquiesce in what is false, we shall never say that he is certain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "I say \"some,\" for they will be better appreciated from what we shall set forth in the fifth part.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Again, those who confuse words with ideas, or with the affirmation which an idea involves, think that they can wish something contrary to what they feel, affirm, or deny.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "This misconception will easily be laid aside by one, who reflects on the nature of knowledge, and seeing that it in no wise involves the conception of extension, will therefore clearly understand, that an idea (being a mode of thinking) does not consist in the image of anything, nor in words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "The essence of words and images is put together by bodily motions, which in no wise involve the conception of thought.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Of these, the first is advanced by those, who think that the will has a wider scope than the understanding, and that therefore it is different therefrom.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Nothing therefore seems to be taught more clearly by experience, than that the will or faculty of assent is free and different from the faculty of understanding.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Thirdly, it may be objected that one affirmation does not apparently contain more reality than another; in other words, that we do not seem to need for affirming, that what is true is true, any greater power than for affirming, that what is false is true.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "We have, however, seen that one idea has more reality or perfection than another, for as objects are some more excellent than others, so also are the ideas of them some more excellent than others; this also seems to point to a difference between the understanding and the will.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000016_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000016_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "If I say that he would not, he would then determine his own action, and would consequently possess the faculty of going and doing whatever he liked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "For instance, the affirmation which involves the idea of a circle, differs from that which involves the idea of a triangle, as much as the idea of a circle differs from the idea of a triangle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "note).",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "We must therefore conclude, that we are easily deceived, when we confuse universals with singulars, and the entities of reason and abstractions with realities.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "The doctrine is good,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Such a doctrine not only completely tranquilizes our spirit, but also shows us where our highest happiness or blessedness is, namely, solely in the knowledge of God, whereby we are led to act only as love and piety shall bid us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "We may thus clearly understand, how far astray from a true estimate of virtue are those who expect to be decorated by God with high rewards for their virtue, and their best actions, as for having endured the direst slavery; as if virtue and the service of God were not in itself happiness and perfect freedom.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24747_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24747/3227_24747_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "I think I have therein explained the nature and properties of the human mind at sufficient length, and, considering the difficulty of the subject, with sufficient clearness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "This love towards God must hold the chief place in the mind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "God is without passions, neither is he affected by any emotion of pleasure or pain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "No one can hate God.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "This love towards God cannot be stained by the emotion of envy or jealousy: contrariwise, it is the more fostered, in proportion as we conceive a greater number of men to be joined to God by the same bond of love.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Note.--We can in the same way show, that there is no emotion directly contrary to this love, whereby this love can be destroyed; therefore we may conclude, that this love towards God is the most constant of all the emotions, and that, in so far as it is referred to the body, it cannot be destroyed, unless the body be destroyed also.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "As to its nature, in so far as it is referred to the mind only, we shall presently inquire.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "I have now gone through all the remedies against the emotions, or all that the mind, considered in itself alone, can do against them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3227_24784_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3227/24784/3227_24784_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3227",
        "content": "Whence it appears that the mind's power over the emotions consists:----",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
